    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You form a whip out of water, holding it together with Chakra. It functions as a normal whip, with which you are automatically proficient. If you use Raite no Jutsu while holding a water whip, you can make its attack with the whip, adding the whip's damage and treating the attack as though the target were wearing metal armor (see Raite no Jutsu).<br><br>The whip immediately loses its form if it leaves your grasp.</p>\n\n\n\n",
